1
00:00:24,199 --> 00:00:24,719
Boss

2
00:00:24,839 --> 00:00:25,920
Why don't we leave now?

3
00:00:26,079 --> 00:00:26,879
It's about time.

4
00:00:28,719 --> 00:00:29,399
Wait a bit longer.

5
00:00:30,600 --> 00:00:31,519
Luo Xiao isn't here yet.

6
00:00:52,719 --> 00:00:53,600
The moment he arrives,

7
00:00:54,039 --> 00:00:54,880
move fast.

8
00:01:04,640 --> 00:01:05,480
Get ready.

9
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:07,680
He's here.

10
00:01:39,159 --> 00:01:39,760
Move.

11
00:01:42,439 --> 00:01:43,480
Hands on your head! Don't move!

12
00:01:58,040 --> 00:01:58,959
This is the last transfer.

13
00:01:59,159 --> 00:01:59,879
There's more.

14
00:02:00,280 --> 00:02:01,000
Easy.

15
00:02:25,159 --> 00:02:25,919
Transfer's done.

16
00:02:34,319 --> 00:02:35,000
Take a look.

17
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:37,240
Do it.

18
00:02:49,879 --> 00:02:51,080
What's going on?

19
00:02:54,599 --> 00:02:55,560
Damn!

20
00:02:56,840 --> 00:02:58,439
A billion for just 200,000?

21
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:01,719
You're so cheap.

22
00:03:02,319 --> 00:03:03,199
Cheap bastard!

23
00:03:03,439 --> 00:03:04,240
Goodbye.

24
00:03:04,840 --> 00:03:05,599
Good riddance.

25
00:03:07,599 --> 00:03:08,719
So damn cheap.

26
00:03:11,520 --> 00:03:12,879
Boss Luo, it's done.

27
00:03:13,120 --> 00:03:14,800
I've wired you the 5 million deposit.

28
00:03:14,919 --> 00:03:17,039
Good. The rest will be in within a week.

29
00:03:17,599 --> 00:03:18,560
Thank you.

30
00:03:19,840 --> 00:03:21,639
I won't say a word about Xin Youna.

31
00:03:21,759 --> 00:03:22,919
Take the money and run.

32
00:03:23,240 --> 00:03:24,360
Don't ever contact me again.

33
00:03:24,520 --> 00:03:25,199
Got it, got it.

34
00:03:29,680 --> 00:03:30,759
Sir, Luo Xiao's car.

35
00:03:43,840 --> 00:03:44,560
On the boat.

36
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:46,719
Follow me.

37
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:47,680
Move in!

38
00:03:56,439 --> 00:03:57,159
Boss Luo.

39
00:04:00,919 --> 00:04:01,599
Ganzi.

40
00:04:01,960 --> 00:04:02,680
Come on, come on.

41
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:11,280
What are you doing?

42
00:04:11,840 --> 00:04:12,560
Ganzi!

43
00:04:16,639 --> 00:04:17,680
Who tipped off the cops?

44
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:19,120
It wasn't me, it wasn't me!

45
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:19,920
Ganzi!

46
00:04:20,040 --> 00:04:21,560
Grab the girl, grab her, grab her!

47
00:04:21,720 --> 00:04:22,680
Hold her down!

48
00:04:23,480 --> 00:04:24,959
We're Jiaohai County Police!

49
00:04:25,879 --> 00:04:26,720
Don't do anything rash!

50
00:04:26,839 --> 00:04:27,839
Drop your weapons!

51
00:04:28,439 --> 00:04:29,160
Zhang Heng.

52
00:04:29,519 --> 00:04:30,439
Don't move!

53
00:04:30,680 --> 00:04:31,879
They've got Paopao.

54
00:04:32,240 --> 00:04:33,439
Uncle.

55
00:04:33,839 --> 00:04:34,560
Paopao!

56
00:04:35,399 --> 00:04:36,120
Back off!

57
00:04:36,839 --> 00:04:38,160
Get back where I can't see you!

58
00:04:38,560 --> 00:04:39,759
I'll stab her!

59
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:42,720
We can talk about your terms.

60
00:04:43,399 --> 00:04:44,720
I can have my men pull back,

61
00:04:45,199 --> 00:04:47,279
but you cannot harm the hostage.

62
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:49,279
As a show of good faith,

63
00:04:49,759 --> 00:04:50,959
release one person first.

64
00:04:51,120 --> 00:04:52,519
I'll pull my men back immediately.

65
00:04:52,759 --> 00:04:53,399
Sir.

66
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:54,800
The sniper is in position.

67
00:04:55,360 --> 00:04:56,839
No, it's too close.

68
00:04:56,959 --> 00:04:58,000
Could hit the hostage.

69
00:04:59,040 --> 00:05:00,360
Let the little girl go.

70
00:05:01,360 --> 00:05:02,839
Release her and we'll pull back.

71
00:05:04,399 --> 00:05:05,439
Listen to me.

72
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:09,240
If you really keep your word,

73
00:05:10,639 --> 00:05:12,360
Ruan Chen paid for my life,

74
00:05:13,800 --> 00:05:14,879
not my daughter's.

75
00:05:15,519 --> 00:05:17,480
No need to get more blood on your hands.

76
00:05:18,000 --> 00:05:18,800
Right?

77
00:05:19,439 --> 00:05:20,639
Yeah, Boss.

78
00:05:21,240 --> 00:05:23,040
200,000 for two lives, we're losing out.

79
00:05:26,560 --> 00:05:28,439
He's got a point.

80
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:31,079
Release the girl now.

81
00:05:37,519 --> 00:05:38,199
Go!

82
00:05:38,839 --> 00:05:39,720
Go on, Paopao!

83
00:05:50,839 --> 00:05:51,480
Ganzi!

84
00:05:51,879 --> 00:05:53,240
Ganzi, start the boat!

85
00:05:56,399 --> 00:05:57,480
Keep your word!

86
00:05:57,680 --> 00:05:58,319
Okay.

87
00:05:58,800 --> 00:05:59,879
Honor your promise.

88
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:01,240
Don't hurt the hostage.

89
00:06:04,720 --> 00:06:05,600
Step back.

90
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:06,959
You better keep your word!

91
00:06:07,120 --> 00:06:07,920
Okay.

92
00:06:08,759 --> 00:06:10,040
Step back.

93
00:06:11,120 --> 00:06:11,879
Back!

94
00:06:13,560 --> 00:06:14,199
Step back.

95
00:06:19,560 --> 00:06:20,879
Tell the sniper to get ready.

96
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:23,639
Sniper.

97
00:06:23,879 --> 00:06:24,759
You're clear to fire.

98
00:06:59,800 --> 00:07:00,600
Shi Qijun

99
00:07:01,199 --> 00:07:03,120
Every contract bears your signature.

100
00:07:08,480 --> 00:07:09,319
What about Luo Xiao?

101
00:07:12,079 --> 00:07:14,120
Luo Xiao must answer for his own actions.

102
00:07:20,879 --> 00:07:23,439
Defendant Luo Xiao, a lawyer,

103
00:07:23,759 --> 00:07:24,879
knowingly broke the law.

104
00:07:25,399 --> 00:07:27,360
Without state authorization,

105
00:07:27,680 --> 00:07:30,319
he illegally conducted fund settlements,

106
00:07:30,519 --> 00:07:32,360
disrupting the national financial order.

107
00:07:32,800 --> 00:07:35,839
His acts constitute illegal business.

108
00:07:36,319 --> 00:07:38,959
The prosecution's charges are upheld.

109
00:07:39,759 --> 00:07:40,720
Defendant Luo Xiao,

110
00:07:40,959 --> 00:07:42,399
in this joint criminal act,

111
00:07:42,560 --> 00:07:43,800
played the principal role,

112
00:07:44,279 --> 00:07:45,319
making him the principal offender.

113
00:07:49,360 --> 00:07:50,680
I always used to think

114
00:07:51,439 --> 00:07:53,399
money was the most important thing.

115
00:07:54,560 --> 00:07:55,399
With money,

116
00:07:56,360 --> 00:07:58,079
any problem could be solved.

117
00:07:58,639 --> 00:07:59,920
No one would look down on you.

118
00:08:00,839 --> 00:08:02,399
You'd have time for family.

119
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:05,240
But slowly, I forgot

120
00:08:06,160 --> 00:08:07,480
what truly matters,

121
00:08:08,519 --> 00:08:09,720
what's most precious.

122
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:23,639
In this case,

123
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:24,519
due to Luo Xiao's involvement,

124
00:08:24,560 --> 00:08:26,480
the source of laundered funds is unclear.

125
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:28,560
The evidence is sufficient to establish

126
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:29,959
his crime of illegal business operations.

127
00:08:30,120 --> 00:08:31,600
Thus, for illegal business operations,

128
00:08:31,639 --> 00:08:33,039
he is hereby convicted and sentenced.

129
00:08:33,440 --> 00:08:35,200
As for the specific source of the funds,

130
00:08:35,399 --> 00:08:37,840
authorities must continue investigating,

131
00:08:38,159 --> 00:08:39,279
thoroughly tracing the money trail

132
00:08:39,320 --> 00:08:40,559
and any related matters.

133
00:08:40,840 --> 00:08:41,720
Based on the testimony,

134
00:08:41,879 --> 00:08:43,679
the court's ruling on all defendants

135
00:08:43,720 --> 00:08:44,720
is as follows.

136
00:09:45,240 --> 00:09:46,279
Tell me,

137
00:09:48,360 --> 00:09:49,879
if I had been the one to take Paopao

138
00:09:49,960 --> 00:09:51,480
on that seaside vacation,

139
00:09:54,879 --> 00:09:56,120
the outcome

140
00:09:59,440 --> 00:10:01,200
wouldn't be like this now, right?

141
00:10:08,000 --> 00:10:09,960
This is the best outcome we could get.

142
00:10:12,320 --> 00:10:13,080
Don't look back.

143
00:10:14,399 --> 00:10:15,440
Let's look ahead.

144
00:10:19,679 --> 00:10:20,679
Tell me,

145
00:10:21,000 --> 00:10:22,840
Luo Xiao made all that money,

146
00:10:24,519 --> 00:10:25,679
didn't he leave any for you?

147
00:10:50,279 --> 00:10:50,960
Honey,

148
00:10:51,519 --> 00:10:52,399
Get in the car.

149
00:10:53,039 --> 00:10:54,240
I'll go check something over there.

150
00:10:55,080 --> 00:10:56,159
Check what?

151
00:10:56,840 --> 00:10:58,840
About Chen Yongjiang and Huang Qiuping.

152
00:11:00,320 --> 00:11:01,200
They're right over there.

153
00:11:01,440 --> 00:11:02,000
Alright.

154
00:11:02,120 --> 00:11:03,200
I'll wait for you in the car then.
